ActCanadian Human Rights Act
PrecisAppointment of KAREN ANN JENSEN of Ottawa, Ontario, to be the full-time member of the Canadian Human Rights Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending on the earlier of September 30, 2020, or the day on which section 419 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2018, No. 2 comes into force, effective October 16, 2019; and to be the Pay Equity Commissioner of the Canadian Human Rights Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, effective on the day on which section 419 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2018, No. 2 comes into force.
